         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Treasury ¶ Melbourne ¶ ,  ¶ July 15th ¶  1864. ¶ A.B. ¶ M ¶ EMORANDUM ¶ —A| ¶ C ¶  ¶ M 1712/13 ¶ Instead of charging a portion of the cost of the Horse to the item for "Incidental Expenses", the prope...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">64.07.15</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Edward Symonds</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">H64/7313, unit 31, VPRS 3991/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>Treasury</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Melbourne</seg>
               <seg style="font-style: italic; ">, </seg>July 15th<seg> 1864.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">A.B.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg>M</seg>
               <seg style="font-size: 10pt; ">EMORANDUM</seg>
               <seg>—A|</seg>
               <seg style="font-size: 10pt; ">C</seg>
               <seg>
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               </seg>M 1712/13</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Instead of charging a portion of the cost of the Horse to the item for "Incidental Expenses", the proper course would be to move the Hon, the Cf Secy<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Chief Secretary.</p>
               </note> to issue a "Transfer authority" to transfer £3 from "Incidentals" to the item, "Purchase of a draught horse", so that the expenditure may be brought under instead.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">E. S Symonds</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">The Director of the Botanic Gardens<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See also M to J. McCulloch, 26 July 1864.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg>N.B.—It is requested that this Memorandum may be returned with the account and reply.</seg>
               <note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">x-ref also to earlier correspondence on this subject.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
